title: Another Xbox Event in August?! - Kinda Funny Games Daily 07.29.20
description:
Time Stamps - 
00:00:00 - Start
00:03:00 - Housekeeping
Avengers Reacts
It’s Major Nelson’s Kinda Funny weekend!
Thursday, join Greg and Major Nelson for We Have Cool Friends.
Friday, Major Nelson joins Greg for Kinda Funny Games Daily.
Saturday, Major Nelson joins Snowbike Mike and Alanah Pearce for the Kinda Funny Xcast.
That all is going down right here on Twitch, youtube.com/KindaFunny, Youtube.com/KindaFunnyGames, and podcast services around the globe.
Thank you to our Patreon Producers:Mohammed Mohammed & Black Jack
The Roper Report   -
00:07:05 - Xbox Event in August?! Joseph patrick @ International Business Times
00:27:22 - Fable Has an All-Star Team, Andy Robinson @ VGC
00:33:43 - Grounded is a Steam Best Seller, Richard Wakeling @GameSpot
00:39:35 - Do you see Sony committing to games like this in the near future or sticking with what's worked so well for them? - Best Friends Q:Shawn Cassidy (aka OtisSpunkmeyer)
00:42:40 - Halo Nerf Gun comes with Halo Infinite DLC, Eddie @ GameSpot
00:45:15 - Private Division Makin Moves, RV @ GIB
00:46:30 - Drinkbox is teasing their new game
00:47:30 -  Brooklinen
00:48:18 - Out today
 Reader mail   -
00:50:48 - Squad Up: Bryan Cacciattolo(Xbox One) - Everater
00:52:30 - You‘re Wrong
Tomorrow’s Hosts: Blessing and special guest: ZombaeKillz
